(N'BACKUPTHREAD',N'BACKUP_RESTORE',2,0,N'Occurs when a task is waiting for a backup task to finish. Wait times may be long, from several minutes to several hours. If the task that is being waited on is in an I/O process, this type does not indicate a problem.',N'Backup-, Restore- oder Medienverarbeitung.',N'Operationen dauern länger; konkurrierender I/O kann beeinflusst werden.',N'Aktive Operation, Throughput, Zielmedium, Stripe und Storage prüfen.',N'REFERENCE_NORMALIZED',N'IMPORTED_REVIEW_REQUIRED'),
(N'BACKUP_OPERATOR',N'BACKUP_RESTORE',2,0,N'Occurs when a task is waiting for a tape mount. To view the tape status, query sys.dm_io_backup_tapes. If a mount operation is not pending, this wait type may indicate a hardware problem with the tape drive.',N'Backup-, Restore- oder Medienverarbeitung.',N'Operationen dauern länger; konkurrierender I/O kann beeinflusst werden.',N'Aktive Operation, Throughput, Zielmedium, Stripe und Storage prüfen.',N'REFERENCE_NORMALIZED',N'IMPORTED_REVIEW_REQUIRED'),
