(N'DBMIRROR_EVENTS_QUEUE',N'HA_REPLICATION',0,1,N'Occurs when database mirroring waits for events to process.',N'Availability Groups, Mirroring oder HA-Hintergrundarbeit.',N'Je Wait entweder erwarteter Idle-Zustand oder erhöhte Commit-/Redo-/Send-Latenz.',N'Benign-Flag beachten; Replica-Zustand, Queues, Netzwerk und Log-I/O prüfen.',N'REFERENCE_NORMALIZED',N'IMPORTED_REVIEW_REQUIRED'),
(N'DBMIRROR_SEND',N'HA_REPLICATION',2,0,N'Occurs when a task is waiting for a communications backlog at the network layer to clear to be able to send messages. Indicates that the communications layer is starting to become overloaded and affect the database mirroring data throughput.',N'Availability Groups, Mirroring oder HA-Hintergrundarbeit.',N'Je Wait entweder erwarteter Idle-Zustand oder erhöhte Commit-/Redo-/Send-Latenz.',N'Benign-Flag beachten; Replica-Zustand, Queues, Netzwerk und Log-I/O prüfen.',N'REFERENCE_NORMALIZED',N'IMPORTED_REVIEW_REQUIRED'),
(N'DBMIRROR_WORKER_QUEUE',N'HA_REPLICATION',0,1,N'Indicates that the database mirroring worker task is waiting for more work.',N'Availability Groups, Mirroring oder HA-Hintergrundarbeit.',N'Je Wait entweder erwarteter Idle-Zustand oder erhöhte Commit-/Redo-/Send-Latenz.',N'Benign-Flag beachten; Replica-Zustand, Queues, Netzwerk und Log-I/O prüfen.',N'REFERENCE_NORMALIZED',N'IMPORTED_REVIEW_REQUIRED'),
